      <title>Meta 预计支出增加引发投资者担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-24/meta-projects-higher-spending-raising-investor-concerns-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 上调了今年的支出预期，并预计第二季度的销售额低于华尔街的预期，这再次引发了人们对其未来技术押注最终能否为投资者带来回报的疑问。第一季度盈利超出预期。收盘后该股大幅下跌。彭博社的埃德·勒德洛报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-24/meta-projects-higher-spending-raising-investor-concerns-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 20:30:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
